  Pages = {26--61},
  R-Shafer90Amai = {The basic algorithms we describe in sections 7 and 8 do not go beyond the algorithms of Kelly and Barclay \cite{Kelly73obhp}, Cannings, Thompson and Skolnick \cite{Cannings78aap}, Pearl \cite{Pearl86ai}, and Lauritzen and Spiegelhalter \cite{Lauritzen88jrssb} in what they accomplish, but they do show that the accomplishment is simpler than sometimes thought.},
