  R-Alekhnovich06Siam = {An elegant upper bound was given by Schoning, who showed that the expected running time of RWalkSAT on any k-CNF is at most (1+1/k)n (compared with the exhaustive search upper bound of 2n) [38]. The (worst case) upper bound of /citet{Schoning99focs} was improved in a sequence of results [..], and the best upper bound for 3-SAT is (1.324)n, given by the recent paper /cite{Iwama04da}.},
